===Comeback=== *Only two teams have lost the first leg of a playoffs or qualifying round match with ten or more points, but still managed to qualify for the next round: **[[Karşıyaka Basket|Karşıyaka]] lost by 10 (90–80) against [[Skyliners Frankfurt]] in the playoffs qualifiers [[2016–17 Basketball Champions League|2016–17]], but won by 20 (72–52) in the second leg and 152–142 on aggregate **[[AEK B.C.|AEK]] lost by 10 (88–98) against [[Basketball Nymburk|Nymburk]] in the round of 16 [[2017–18 Basketball Champions League|2017–18]], but won by 11 (82–93) in the second leg and 181–180 on aggregate *In the qualifying rounds, [[Donar (basketball club)|Donar]] lost by 20 (84–64) against [[KB Prishtina|Prishtina]] in the first leg, but won by 25 (80–55) in the second leg and 144–139 in the aggregate.
