===Consecutive home wins=== [[AS Monaco|Monaco]] holds the record with 17 consecutive home wins in the Champions League. Its run started in the [[2016–17 Basketball Champions League|2016–17]] regular season first round and ended in the [[2017–18 Basketball Champions League|2017–18]] quarterfinals second leg.
===Consecutive away wins=== [[AS Monaco|Monaco]] holds the record with 7 consecutive away wins in the Champions League. Its run started in the [[2016–17 Basketball Champions League|2016–17]] quarterfinals first leg and ended in the [[2017–18 Basketball Champions League|2017–18]] regular season round 14.
===Consecutive wins=== [[AS Monaco Basket|Monaco]] holds the record of 14 consecutive wins in the Champions League. Its run started in the [[2016–17 Basketball Champions League|2016–17]] third place game and ended in the [[2017–18 Basketball Champions League|2017–18]] round 14.
